            "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"><title>QuickBite</title><style>:root{--bg:#FFF8F0;--card:#FFF;--accent:#FF8C69;--text:#4A3E38;--muted:#A1887F;--radius:16px;--space:20px}*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body{font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.6;font-size:16px}html,body{width:100%;max-width:375px;margin:0 auto;height:100vh}header{background:var(--card);padding:var(--space);border-bottom:1px solid #F0E6E0;text-align:center}header h1{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:4px}header p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted)}.hero{padding:var(--space);text-align:center}.hero h2{font-size:24px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:12px}.hero p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:var(--space)}.cta-button{display:inline-block;background:var(--accent);color:#FFF;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:var(--radius);border:none;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.2s}.cta-button:hover{background:#E67A57}.recipe-grid{padding:var(--space);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space)}.recipe-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:var(--space);border:1px solid #F0E6E0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(74,62,56,0.08)}.recipe-card h3{font-size:20px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px}.recipe-card .time{font-size:14px;color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}.recipe-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:12px}.recipe-card .ingredients{font-size:13px;color:var(--text);background:#FAFAF8;padding:12px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px}.recipe-card .ingredients strong{display:block;margin-bottom:6px;color:var(--accent)}.recipe-image{width:100%;height:160px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--bg));border-radius:var(--radius);margin-bottom:var(--space)}</style></head><body><header><h1>QuickBite</h1><p>Cooking for people who don't like cooking</p></header><section class=\"hero\"><h2>Hungry but lazy?</h2><p>15-minute recipes that actually taste good. No fuss, no mess.</p><button class=\"cta-button\">Find a Recipe</button></section><section class=\"recipe-grid\"><div class=\"recipe-card\"><div class=\"recipe-image\"></div><h3>Garlic Butter Pasta</h3><div class=\"time\">12 minutes</div><p>Boil pasta, toss with butter, garlic, and parmesan. Done.</p><div class=\"ingredients\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong>Pasta, butter, garlic, parmesan, salt</div></div><div class=\"recipe-card\"><div class=\"recipe-image\"></div><h3>Sheet Pan Chicken</h3><div class=\"time\">18 minutes</div><p>Throw chicken and veggies on a pan. Roast. Eat.</p><div class=\"ingredients\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong>Chicken breast, broccoli, olive oil, lemon, salt</div></div><div class=\"recipe-card\"><div class=\"recipe-image\"></div><h3>Egg Fried Rice</h3><div class=\"time\">10 minutes</div><p>Leftover rice, scrambled eggs, soy sauce. Minimal cleanup.</p><div class=\"ingredients\"><strong>Ingredients:</strong>Rice, eggs, soy sauce, oil, green onions</div></div></section></body></html>",
